    "description": "Against Great Darkness是一款砖块打破roguelike游戏。您是异教神话的典范，试图逃脱魔鬼路西法的控制。战斗通过恶魔实体的波浪并获取伟大的文物，这有助于您逃脱。偶然遇到独特的事件，可以奖励或阻碍您的上升。在每次运行时收集碎片以解锁升级，以提高您的机会。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302150/extras/d34589896e33987cd8750de3c8fab0cb.poster.avif?t=1747247541\" width=630 height=802 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302150/extras/d34589896e33987cd8750de3c8fab0cb.webm?t=1747247541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302150/extras/d34589896e33987cd8750de3c8fab0cb.mp4?t=1747247541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>一块块地打破地狱:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>3个地狱圈要探索<br></li><li>不同的恶魔老板和敌人<br></li><li>每次逃离地狱都是独特的。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302150/extras/e7c86eb63fa1bf26298256a97a2b8c43.poster.avif?t=1747247541\" width=616 height=410 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302150/extras/e7c86eb63fa1bf26298256a97a2b8c43.webm?t=1747247541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302150/extras/e7c86eb63fa1bf26298256a97a2b8c43.mp4?t=1747247541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>成为光之灯塔:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>在独特的事件中做出选择以获得强大的遗物。<br></li><li>物品根据游戏玩法提供独特的修改器。<br></li><li>使用众多物品协同建立您的构建<br></li><li>在每次运行中解锁角色、物品和更多内容。<br></li><li>通过升级您的典范在运行之间增加您的机会</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302150/extras/ee346fab4f5559929f6ad4743db9d139.poster.avif?t=1747247541\" width=630 heigh